  "texts": [
    "Fortunately, AI can deal with these issues in a data-driven manner.",
    "In this section, we present a comprehensive comparison between the modelbased methods and AI-based counterparts in system design and optimization for ISAC.",
    "Furthermore, the motivation of introducing AI to ISAC is also highlighted.",
    "System designModel-based system designs for ISAC follow the modular principle, dividing the whole system into several independent blocks, such as transmitter, channel, and receiver, to individually optimize.",
    "This approach is effective and manageable and has been widely adopted."
  ]
